    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本商品是《女神异闻录３》《女神异闻录４》《女神异闻录５》制作班底的全新作品，幻想风格RPG《暗喻幻想：ReFantazio》的免费体验版。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您可在本体验版中游玩游戏正式版开篇部分的内容。在正式版中可继承本体验版中创建的保存数据，保留角色的能力值，继续游玩体验版的后续剧情。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在被异形怪物“人类”的威胁笼罩的世界中，为了解救好友王子，解开他身上的死亡诅咒，主角踏上了旅途。他将参加竞选，成为新王候选人，开启一段跌宕起伏的旅程。在本体验版中您可体验这段旅程的开篇部分。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130330/extras/9936121ddfb64319a342c329b8183099.poster.avif?t=1763531214\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130330/extras/9936121ddfb64319a342c329b8183099.webm?t=1763531214\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130330/extras/9936121ddfb64319a342c329b8183099.mp4?t=1763531214\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作中搭载了全新的战斗系统“FAST &amp; SQUAD”。您可自由组合超过40种的职业“阿基态”，攻击敌人的弱点，体验充满策略性和紧张感的回合制指令战斗。主角变强后，还可通过动作战斗在场地中快速消灭弱小的敌人。在本体验版中您可简单体验本作的全新战斗系统，以舒适的节奏爽快地探索迷宫，同时还能深入思考如何构建队伍。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130330/extras/67c08dd0b264aecb0772942cb8711978.poster.avif?t=1763531214\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130330/extras/67c08dd0b264aecb0772942cb8711978.webm?t=1763531214\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130330/extras/67c08dd0b264aecb0772942cb8711978.mp4?t=1763531214\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在本体验版中，您可体验本作开篇部分的众多要素。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为解开好友王子身上的死亡诅咒而踏上旅途的故事开篇部分</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >故事开篇的4个迷宫</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可解锁超过40种的职业“阿基态”中的7种</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可邂逅6名在旅途中援助主角的队伍成员及支持者</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130330/extras/b5ef048fc28b18839df758331dec5006.poster.avif?t=1763531214\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130330/extras/b5ef048fc28b18839df758331dec5006.webm?t=1763531214\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3130330/extras/b5ef048fc28b18839df758331dec5006.mp4?t=1763531214\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
